  "text": "A recent review focusing on effective behavioral strategies for C-OCD has suggested that traditional methods of exposure treatment, including exposure and response prevention (ERP; [CITATION_1] , are not always effective for reducing the experience of disgust [CITATION_2] . Thus, additional research is required to further the understanding of exposure treatment methods in C-OCD.",
